" Set line numbers
set relativenumber
"set number

" Move up and down on visible lines
nmap j gj
nmap k gk

" Replace Esc with jk
imap jk <Esc>

" Scroll forward and backward with F (forward) and U (upward)
nmap F <C-f>
nmap U <C-b>

" Move more horizontally
nmap W 6w
nmap B 6b

" Previous position and new position
nmap P <C-o>
nmap N <C-i>
